OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid-19: Masks no longer  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frequired in NI post-primary
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fschools                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Post-primary pupils in Northern Ireland
OL,6, will no longer need to wear face       
OL,7, coverings in classrooms.               
OL,9,FMasks had been a requirement for pupils
OL,10,Fsince the start of term in August 2021.
OL,12,FBut the education minister announced   
OL,13,Fshe was removing the requirement from  
OL,14,F21 March.                              
OL,16,FIt brings Northern Ireland into line   
OL,17,Fwith the rest of the UK and the        
OL,18,FRepublic of Ireland, where similar     
OL,19,Fguidance for school pupils has been    
OL,20,Fadopted.                               
